10/https://www.newyorker.com/news/letter-from-the-uk/the-soundtrack-to-londons-murders|archive-date=24 July 2019|url-status=live}}</ref>\n*Burner<ref name=\"capitalxtra.com\"/>\n*CB<ref name=\"thetimes.co.uk\">{{Cite web|url=https://www.thetimes.co.uk/article/do-drills-lyrics-inspire-knife-crime-or-give-voice-to-a-generation-thats-been-let-down-nqqvjzqdv|title=Do drill\u2019s lyrics inspire knife crime? Or give voice to a generation that\u2019s been let down?|first=Ben|last=Machell|date=4 May 2019|via=www.thetimes.co.uk|access-date=7 August 2019|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190807025017/https://www.thetimes.co.uk/article/do-drills-lyrics-inspire-knife-crime-or-give-voice-to-a-generation-thats-been-let-down-nqqvjzqdv|archive-date=7 August 2019|url-status=live}}</ref>\n*Digga D<ref name=\"capitalxtra.com\"/>\n*DigDat<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.capitalxtra.com/artists/future/news/digdat-song-uk-drill-collab/|title=Future's Collab With UK Drill Rapper DigDat Teased In New Video|website=Capital XTRA|access-date=7 August 2019|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190807025011/https://www.capitalxtra.com/artists/future/news/digdat-song-uk-drill-collab/|archive-date=7 August 2019|url-status=live}}</ref>\n*[[67 (rap group)|Dimzy]]\n*Drillminister <ref>{{cite news|url=https://drillminister.com/2018/11/05/rapper-proves-mps-know-the-drill-on-violent-talk/|work=[[Drillminister]]|title=Rapper proves MPs know the drill on violent talk|date=2018-11-05}}</ref>\n*Frosty <ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.getsurrey.co.uk/news/surrey-news/drill-artist-frosty-who-sang-16128869 |work=Surrey Live |title=Making the banned: Drill artist Frosty who sang about drug dealing jailed over Guildford county lines operation \u2013 Get Surrey |date=15 Aug 2019 |access-date=15 August 2019 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190815102706/https://www.getsurrey.co.uk/news/surrey-news/drill-artist-frosty-who-sang-16128869 |archive-date=15 August 2019 |url-status=live }}</ref>\n*