birminghammail|access-date=7 August 2019|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190807025023/https://www.birminghammail.co.uk/news/midlands-news/notorious-drill-gang-stand-cash-15626704|archive-date=7 August 2019|url-status=live}}</ref>\n*410<ref name=\"Skengdo and AM: the drill rappers\">{{Cite web|url=https://www.theguardian.com/music/2019/jan/31/skengdo-and-am-the-drill-rappers-sentenced-for-playing-their-song|title=Skengdo and AM: the drill rappers sentenced for playing their song|first=Dan|last=Hancox|date=31 January 2019|via=www.theguardian.com|access-date=7 August 2019|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190809083127/https://www.theguardian.com/music/2019/jan/31/skengdo-and-am-the-drill-rappers-sentenced-for-playing-their-song|archive-date=9 August 2019|url-status=live}}</ref>\n*[[67 (rap group)|67]]\n*[[Ghetto Boys|814]]<ref name=\"metro.co.uk\">{{Cite web|url=https://metro.co.uk/2018/08/08/drill-music-linked-violent-crime-london-7812930/|title=What is drill music and why is it linked to violent crime in London?|date=8 August 2018|access-date=7 August 2019|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190806064345/https://metro.co.uk/2018/08/08/drill-music-linked-violent-crime-london-7812930/|archive-date=6 August 2019|url-status=live}}</ref>\n*86<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.vice.com/en_us/article/a3m7nk/uk-drill-holiday-guide|title=A Guide to Explaining UK Drill to Your Family Over the Holidays|first=Tshepo|last=Mokoena|date=20 December 2018|access-date=7 August 2019|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190807014009/https://www.vice.com/en_us/article/a3m7nk/uk-drill-holiday-guide|archive-date=7 August 2019|url-status=live}}</ref>\n*Block 6<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.highsnobiety.com/p/pornhub-hosting-drill-rap-videos/|title=Pornhub Is Now Hosting Banned U.K. Drill Rap Videos|date=10 July 2018|website=Highsnobiety|access-date=7 August 2019|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190807025015/https://www.highsnobiety.com/p/pornhub-hosting-drill-rap-videos/|archive-date=7 August 2019|url-status=live}}</ref>\n*B Side/785\n*CGM (formerly \"1011\")\n*ClapTown\n*[[Harlem Spartans]]<ref name=\"Skengdo and AM: the drill rappers\"/>\n*Hope Dealers<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.itv.com/news/2018-09-07/the-rappers-using-gospel-drill-to-save-youths-from-street-violence/|work=[[ITV News]]|title=Rappers using \u2018gospel drill\u2019 to save youths from street violence|date=2018-09-07|access-date=29 April 2019|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190429045236/https://www.itv.com/news/2018-09-07/the-rappers-using-gospel-drill-to-save-youths-from-street-violence/|archive-date=29 April 2019|url-status=live}}</ref>\n*LTH (Lower Tulse Hill)<ref name=\"standard.co.uk\">{{Cite web|url=https://www.standard.co.uk/news/crime/these-artists-have-a-story-to-tell-music-producer-rejects-calls-to-ban-drill-music-videos-from-the-a3991851.html|title='Knife crime epidemic is bigger problem than just drill music'|date=16 November 2018|website=Evening Standard|access-date=7 August 2019|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190501171947/https://www.standard.co.uk/news/crime/these-artists-have-a-story-to-tell-music-producer-rejects-calls-to-ban-drill-music-videos-from-the-a3991851.html|archive-date=1 May 2019|url-status=live}}</ref>\n*Moscow17\n*M20<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://news.sky.com/story/teenage-drill-rapper-jailed-for-stabbing-boy-15-outside-chicken-shop-11775822|title=Teenage drill rapper jailed for stabbing boy, 15, outside chicken shop|website=Sky News|access-date=7 August 2019|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190807025011/https://news.sky.com/story/teenage-drill-rapper-jailed-for-stabbing-boy-15-outside-chicken-shop-11775822|archive-date=7 August 2019|url-status=live}}</ref>\n*NGang\n*[[Tottenham Mandem|NPK]] (Northumberland Park Killers)<ref name=\"standard.co.uk\"/>\n*[[OFB (group)|OFB (Original Farm Boys)]]\n*Silwood Nation<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/uk-45824358|title=Drill rapper jailed over county lines scam|first=Michael|last=Buchanan|date=12 October 2018|via=www.bbc.co.uk|access-date=12 December 2019|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190811142450/https://www.bbc.com/news/uk-45824358|archive-date=11 August 2019|url-status=live}}</ref>\n*Siraq/727<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.factmag.com/2017/04/27/uk-drill-chicago-brixton/|title=From Chicago to Brixton: The surprising rise of UK drill|date=27 April 2017|access-date=7 August 2019|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190529054414/https://www.factmag.com/2017/04/27/uk-drill-chicago-brixton/|archive-date=29 May 2019|url-status=live}}</ref>\n*[[Russ (UK rapper)|SMG/Splash/M Splash]]\n*[[Zone 2 (music group)|Zone 2]]\n{{div col end}}\n\nNotable artists of UK drill include:\n{{div col|colwidth=18em}}\n*A1FromThe9<ref name=\"capitalxtra.com\">{{Cite web|url=https://www.capitalxtra.com/features/lists/uk-drill-rappers-snapchat-usernames/|title=UK Drill Rappers Snapchat Usernames: The Ultimate List|website=Capital XTRA|access-date=7 August 2019|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190807022756/https://www.capitalxtra.com/features/lists/uk-drill-rappers-snapchat-usernames/|archive-date=7 August 2019|url-status=live}}</ref>\n*Abra Cadabra<ref name=\"capitalxtra.com\"/>\n*AM<ref name=\"capitalxtra.com\"/>\n*ASAP<ref name=\"capitalxtra.com\"/>\n*Blanco<ref name=\"capitalxtra.com\"/>\n*BT<ref name=\"newyorker.com\">{{Cite web|url=https://www.newyorker.com/news/letter-from-the-uk/the-soundtrack-to-londons-murders|title=The Soundtrack to London\u2019s Murders|first=Cond\u00e9|last=Nast|website=The New Yorker|access-date=7 August 2019|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190724013810/https://www.newyorker.com/news/letter-from-the-uk/the-soundtrack-to-londons-murders|archive-date=24 July 2019|url-status=live}}</ref>\n*Burner<ref name=\"capitalxtra.com\"/>\n*CB<ref name=\"thetimes.co.uk\">{{Cite web|url=https://www.thetimes.co.uk/article/do-drills-lyrics-inspire-knife-crime-or-give-voice-t